510  ### 6.1 Bridge Architecture
511  
512  The Bridge is a WebSocket connection from the user's local machine to the SUNy server.
513  
514  **Bridge connection lifecycle:**
515  1. User downloads/installs bridge agent (Node.js script or binary)
516  2. Bridge generates setup code (or user enters one)
517  3. Bridge connects to `wss://suny.technodel.tech/bridge`
518  4. Server registers in `bridgeManager` (keyed by userId)
519  5. All file/shell tool calls are forwarded to bridge
520  6. Bridge executes on user's machine, returns result
521  7. Bridge auto-reconnects on disconnect

